You are not refining prompts.

You are engineering capability amplification.

GLOBAL MISSION

For each of the following systems:

Advanced Analytics

AI Chatbot

A/B Testing

Email Marketing

Team Collaboration

API Management

Custom Integrations

Dashboard Code Editor

